flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens Student Progress] --> B[Show 3 tier tables]
    B --> C[Masterclass]
    B --> D[Online]
    B --> E[Starter Kit]

    C --> F[Choose one student]
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F --> G[Open 3-dot action menu]
    G --> H[Completed Lesson]
    G --> I[Assignment]
    G --> J[Certificate]

    H --> K[Load completed lesson detail]
    K --> L{Reset progress?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Show confirm and reset lesson progress]
    L -->|No| N[Stay on page]

    I --> O[Load assignment detail]
    O --> P{Choose action}
    P -->|Save| Q[Save assignment status or feedback]
    P -->|Send Email| R[Send manual assignment email]
    P -->|Delete Video| S[Confirm then clear assignment video]

    J --> T[Load certificate detail]
    T --> U{Choose action}
    U -->|Generate| V[Create certificate record and file]
    U -->|Send Graduation Email| W[Send graduation email]
    U -->|Recreate| X[Create new certificate version]
    U -->|Download| Y[Download file]
    U -->|Delete| Z[Confirm then soft delete certificate]
